sequenceDiagram
    actor Usuario
    participant ClienteController
    participant Validation as Bean Validation
    participant ApiExceptionHandler

    Usuario->>ClienteController: POST /clientes\npayload inválido
    ClienteController->>Validation: validar ClienteRequest
    Validation-->>ClienteController: MethodArgumentNotValidException
    ClienteController->>ApiExceptionHandler: trata exceção
    ApiExceptionHandler-->>Usuario: 400 Bad Request\nErroResponse + validations
